Test Case ID: TC-005

Title:
Verify user cannot log in with an empty password

Preconditions:
1. User is on the Sauce Demo login page.

Test Steps:
1. Enter "standard_user" into the Username field.
2. Leave the Password field blank.
3. Click the Login button.

Expected Result:
1. User remains on the login page.
2. User is not authenticated.
3. Access to the Inventory page is denied.
4. An error message saying "Epic sadface: Password is required" is displayed.
